-- 
Casino to Close Nine Leader Price Stores, Sell Six, Echos Says

-- B y   M e l i s s a   P o z s g a y
-- 
2011-10-03T05:22:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/casino-to-close-nine-leader-price-stores-sell-six-echos-says.html
Casino Guichard-Perrachon SA (CO)  plans
to close nine of the Leader Price stores it owns and sell
another five to franchisers,  Les Echos  reported without
identifying its sources.  A further Leader Price store is being sold and will change
businesses, the newspaper said. The moves will result in 94 job
losses, according to Les Echos.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
Melissa Pozsgay at   mpozsgay@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  